title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 355: Featuring Darnell Nurse
description:
On Episode 355 of Spittin’ Chiclets the guys are joined by Darnell Nurse. Darnell joined (01:47:20) to discuss playing in Edmonton, living with Connor McDavid, and the upcoming Olympics. The guys also open the show talking about Biz and his TNT debut this week, the guys then dive into their Western Conference preview. The boys wrap up talking about “the worst movie ever” according to Ryan Whitney.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
